dialogue.name: C'mon, one song? I expected a full ass week here! Two more, right now, dudes!
Daddy would LOVE this stage. The helmet girl better let us take the rest of our crew here one day.
We gotta start popping into more places like this with actual musicians.
They called our song `Weird and Raunchy`. Pfft, that was tame as hell. They'd piss themsevles if they heard the love song I wrote for you in the Literature Club.
Ugh, forget that one. I looked like an absolute dipshit.
